{"tid":545572,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"挑！呢啲先叫霸氣囉","createTime":"2018-01-30T15:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T03:23:41.000Z","uid":166518,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"14673b2006af7e27bc58f10fd79665338d217b4d","tid":545572,"uid":166518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"歡迎各位巴絲打全面進場...<br />\n<br />\n話說細佬係連登見到好多 po 都係咁踩一啲非名牌院校。（真奇怪）於是就屎忽痕想開個 po 分享一段幾有趣既親身經歷...<br />\n<br />\n又話說細佬當年屎忽痕（真係純粹屎忽痕）想搵樣有興趣既 topic 繼續進修，於是走左去樹仁讀心理學（part time) <br />\n<br />\n有日細佬準備放工兼返學之際，咁岩撞到個同事行埋黎打招呼...<br />\n<br />\n同事：「乜今日咁早就閃啦？」<br />\n我：「係呀，我趕住返學呀。」<br />\n同事：「咁勤力？讀咩呀？」<br />\n我：「心理學」<br />\n同事：「嘩！好勁呀！係邊間讀呀？」<br />\n我：「樹仁」<br />\n係呢個時候，我同事個樣真係超級驚訝，然後就問：「下？樹仁？點解揀呢間呀？」<br />\n我心諗奇怪啦，樹仁有乜問題？然後我就問我同事：「樹仁有鬼呀？點解唔揀得？」<br />\n同事：「唔係，不過樹仁唔多出名，排名又唔高，點解唔揀其他大學呀？」<br />\n我：「挑！有我入去讀，佢間野排名就自然高架啦！呢啲咪叫霸氣囉！」<br />\n同事：「勁！」<br />\n<br />\n當然成件事對我來講都只係笑話一場。不過亦可以側面反映出有好多人都認為名牌效應既重要性。社會對非名牌大學既學生的確存在著一定程度既偏見或岐視。對學生做成一定程度既壓力或影響..."},{"pid":"013da0c69f4e0420b2b48d1f10dc8de4bc15de3a","tid":545572,"uid":158660,"like":22,"dislike":8,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e2351bd897237601be6140e5952c253f4e413e0","tid":545572,"uid":55375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"吓？樹仁？點解揀呢間呀？"},{"pid":"28453f7700c08fbb5c0d4d0e81e979b49604b7bd","tid":545572,"uid":157899,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"好有即刻駁嘴既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b868964bb2bb6d255e832c08b189e848095f187b","tid":545572,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多"},{"pid":"b4620ffb5c3fe9ad0809e548f1f9db296f9ca59b","tid":545572,"uid":166857,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"見到樹仁兩隻字就冇睇落去sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef238deec5d3f1d6c068c6b67c6c77decec6ddcb","tid":545572,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02739fa267c8807756f06f994087f4eb649ccbc6","tid":545572,"uid":71425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"即刻博咀"},{"pid":"37603e7eae6c66e690a9fbbbd3e1ea8e807edee6","tid":545572,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2247beb517ef8545e413d8bb58f144fe76785aa1","tid":545572,"uid":151349,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"013da0c69f4e0420b2b48d1f10dc8de4bc15de3a","tid":545572,"uid":158660,"like":22,"dislike":8,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:47:17.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"65edccef5ec2a271aa4349c0a6dd686799b33776","tid":545572,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"樓豬巧能型，搞到小妹睇到濕左^^"},{"pid":"4b2135b2bed8a3d538232fef04f4642635f21683","tid":545572,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"為左吸收新知識，咁名牌學校自然多資源，對學習一定有幫助。<br />\n如果為左識人，咁名牌學校一定多D社會地位比較高既人去讀。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，我個人覺得學費都係一個好重要因素&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7033672898725f88f19f1ed70855740d421972e6","tid":545572,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:23:41.000Z","msg":"「勁！」"}]}